title: Woof! Bark! Meow! Pets Allowed Here! Check us out!
posting_body: ['Hello Apartments', '9201 Golden Valley Rd', 'Golden Valley, MN 55427', 'show contact info', 'Unit Information:', '1 Bedroom | 1 Bath', 'Unit Size:', '588 sq ft', 'Monthly Rent:', '$1330', 'Lease Terms:', '12-Month', 'Unit Includes:', '❖ Disposal', '❖ Efficient Appliances', '❖ Extra Storage', '❖ In-Home Laundry Room', '❖ Large Closets', '❖ Luxury Vinyl Plank Flooring', '❖ Patio/Balcony', '❖ Polished Quartz Countertops', '❖ Refrigerator', '❖ Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Property Description:', 'Offering well-designed one- and two-bedroom apartment homes with remarkable interior features such as polished quartz countertops and luxury vinyl plank flooring, and expansive walk-in closets- schedule an appointment to come and see for yourself.', "At Hello, you'll enjoy access to the city, unmatched urban amenities, and all the beauty of Golden Valley.", 'Enjoy an activity-filled weekend indoors or out.', 'Hello Apartments features a lobby bar and second-floor clubroom with games, comfortable seating as well as a full kitchen for private get-togethers or resident events such as cooking demos and holiday celebrations.', 'Hello is proudly managed by Peak Living.', 'At Peak Living, our mission is to provide the highest quality property management services in the industry.', 'We achieve this through our greatest asset; our people.', 'Our on-site and regional management teams offer unsurpassed customer service and local expertise for those living at our properties and for our clients.', 'Our experiences and entrepreneurial spirit mean that we understand that no two buildings or clients are the same, and as such, flexibility and adaptability are key to achieving investment goals.', 'Through the use of the latest technologies, Peak Living is able to provide exceptional accounting/reporting as well as industry-leading portal functionality for prospective and current residents, including digital lease signing, online work order submission, and online payments.', 'Property Amenities:', '❖ BBQ/Picnic Area', '❖ Business Center', '❖ Clubhouse', '❖ Courtyard', '❖ Dog Run', '❖ Fitness Center', '❖ Pool', '❖ Volleyball Court', '❖ Availability 24 Hours', '❖ Laundry Facilities', '❖ On-Site Maintenance', '❖ On-Site Management', '❖ Package Receiving', 'Website:', '<URL>/', 'Call us today!', 'show contact info', 'Mon - Fri: 9:00 AM - 6:00 PM', 'Pet Ownership Policy:', 'Allowed: 2 Pet Limit.', 'Proudly managed by Peak Living', 'EQUAL HOUSING OPPORTUNITY', '6FE67CB19AEA42E']
